verbose_text: Whereas there is little fluctuation in the direction of UNC-40 localization in wild-type animals, and much fluctuation in the UNC-40 (A1056V) and unc-53; unc-6 experiments, in these mutants the fluctuation is intermediate with a ventral bias.
